\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0 After we've moved our scene to where we want it, we can get rid of the placeholder by clicking on the 'Narrative hook' plot point once more and then clicking the }{\f5\fs24\b1\i0 Delete }{\f2\fs24\b0\i0 button.}
