\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0 We also have an idea of what our climax scene is\hich\f2 \emdash \loch\f2   the showdown we visualized when we were thinking about our problem's resolution.  Clicking on the 'Climax' plot point, change the description to 'Tony diverts Lacas with the phone and wounds him.'   The idea is that Tony calls Lacas' phone, which interrupts him.}
